column6: A trip to the Negative Zone goes awry when Annihilus shows up to make trouble. Reed and crew are locked in a battle for their very lives against a foe whose powers just might surpass their own. And it's all part of Reed's plan.
column8: | penciller (cover):Jim Cheung | writer:Robert Kirkman | penciller:Cliff Rathburn | letterer:Clem Robins
